OL,3,CWill you get money back as water firms
OL,4,Cordered to return #158m to customers?
OL,6,FWater woes: Leaks, supply
OL,7,Finterruptions, missed pollution
OL,8,Ftargets and falling customer
OL,9,Fsatisfaction leave Ofwat
OL,10,F'disappointed' in water companies
OL,11,Ffollowing annual review
OL,13,FWater firms have been ordered to pay
OL,14,F#157.6 million back to customers after
OL,15,Fmissing key targets on pollution,
OL,16,Fleaks, supply interruptions and
OL,17,Ffalling customer satisfaction.
