OL,3,CWill you get money back as water firms
OL,4,Cordered to return #158m to customers?
OL,6,FOfwat, the water regulator, has judged
OL,7,Feach of the water companies and found
OL,8,Fthat none met the criteria for their
OL,9,Ftop category of "leading".
OL,11,FAnglian Water, Welsh Water and
OL,12,FSouthern Water fell into its lowest
OL,13,Fcategory of "lagging", while the
OL,14,Fremaining 10 were awarded an "average"
OL,15,Frating.
OL,17,FBosses at the regulator judge the
OL,18,Fperformance of water firms each year
OL,19,Fagainst "stretching targets" they set
OL,20,Fin 2019 for a five-year period until
OL,21,F2025.
