OL,3,CWill you get money back as water firms
OL,4,Cordered to return #158m to customers?
OL,6,FFailure to meet those targets results
OL,7,Fin Ofwat restricting the amount of
OL,8,Fmoney they can take from customers.
OL,10,FCustomers won't need to chase the
OL,11,Fmoney owed by water firms, their bills
OL,12,Fwill instead be amended to reflect the
OL,13,Fdecision made by the water regulator.
OL,15,FOfwat has said the figures are
OL,16,Fprovisional until it completes a
OL,17,Freview process in December - the exact
OL,18,Famount that will be returned to
OL,19,Fcustomers will also be finalised then.
