OL,6,FWhich water firms have to pay back the
OL,7,Fmost to their customers?
OL,9,FWhile no firm ranked above "average",
OL,10,FSES Water, Northumbria Water, Severn
OL,11,FTrent Water and United Utilities
OL,12,Foutperformed payments .
OL,14,FDavid Black, chief executive of Ofwat,
OL,15,Fsaid: "This year's performance report
OL,16,Fis stark evidence that money alone
OL,17,Fwill not bring the sustained
OL,18,Fimprovements that customers rightly
OL,19,Fexpect.
