OL,6,F"As we look towards the next price
OL,7,Fcontrol, the challenge for water
OL,8,Fcompanies is to match the investment
OL,9,Fwith the changes in company culture
OL,10,Fand performance that are essential to
OL,11,Fdeliver lasting change."
OL,13,FThames Water, which has been beset
OL,14,Fwith financial woes, and has continued
OL,15,Fto sink further and further into
OL,16,Fhundreds of millions worth of debt had
OL,17,Fsome rare good news in that it was
OL,18,Flifted from "lagging" to "average"
OL,19,Fafter meeting performance targets on
OL,20,Fleaks and supply.
