OL,6,FPenalties are separate to an ongoing
OL,7,FOfwat investigation into all 11 of
OL,8,FEngland and Wales's water firms, which
OL,9,Fordered three companies to pay #168
OL,10,Fmillion in fines in August, in the
OL,11,Ffirst results of the probe.
OL,13,FIt comes against a backdrop of
OL,14,Fmounting public and political fury at
OL,15,Fthe privatised water sector which is
OL,16,Funder fire over sewage spills,
OL,17,Fproposed bill rises and executive
OL,18,Fbonuses.
