OL,6,FYears of under-investment by the
OL,7,Fprivately-run firms combined with
OL,8,Fageing water infrastructure, a growing
OL,9,Fpopulation and more extreme weather
OL,10,Fcaused by climate change have seen the
OL,11,Fquality of England's rivers, lakes and
OL,12,Foceans plummet in recent years.
